Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.13,Translation,,0,0,0,,The 20 rules are buried, the 10 commandments crushed, even public facts submerged
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:05.91,Translation,,0,0,0,,In other words: it defies prediction at every turn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.91,0:00:11.30,Translation,,0,0,0,,Yet calamity doth approach: all over, catastrophes are born screaming, trials strummed by my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.60,Translation,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to have that idiotic mentality?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:16.46,Translation,,0,0,0,,There is not a morsel for you to peck at!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:19.55,Translation,,0,0,0,,Come now, drown in endless anguish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:27.56,Translation,,0,0,0,,Starve to death while clutching at ways to reach the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:30.71,Translation,,0,0,0,,As the moon crosses the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:34.03,Translation,,0,0,0,,the waves grow enraged
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:37.12,Translation,,0,0,0,,The cries of seagulls
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:40.67,Translation,,0,0,0,,beckon the turbulent clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:43.95,Translation,,0,0,0,,The golden curse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.95,Translation,,0,0,0,,the words left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:50.23,Translation,,0,0,0,,and the secretive smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.54,Translation,,0,0,0,,all become smeared with crimson
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:01:00.44,Translation,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for, with your eyes sealed shut?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:06.30,Translation,,0,0,0,,Try as you may to collect the shattered fragments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:10.40,Translation,,0,0,0,,they shall spill from the hands that touch them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:13.29,Translation,,0,0,0,,and never reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:16.39,Translation,,0,0,0,,The tapestry of truth and lies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:18.44,Translation,,0,0,0,,Without love, it cannot be ‘seen’
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:26.70,Translation,,0,0,0,,Without love, without love, you won’t see the truth
